column2: SELECT TOP # A.ra, A.dec, D.ra, D.dec, B.distance, A.objID, B.objID as objIDMatch, C.objID as objIDJOIN, A.specobjID, C.specobjID as specobjIDJOIN, D.specobjID as specobjIDClean FROM SpecPhotoAll AS A CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (C.ra, C.dec, #/#.) AS B LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as C on B.objID = C.objID LEFT JOIN SpecObj as D on C.specobjID = D.specobjID WHERE D.class! =# AND A.specobjID! =C.specobjID AND B.distance> # INTO MyDB.SpecMatch
